title: Wendi McLendon-Covey
itunes:title: Wendi McLendon-Covey
itunes:subtitle: Wendi McLendon-Covey [The Goldbergs, Bridesmaids, Reno 911!] is an actress, comedian, and producer. Wendi talks with Anna about being a teenage dance teacher, her fear of snakes, love of wolves, a jewelry store heist gone bad, Pippi Longstocking and more!
